"title": "4466: herbs and spices",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4466: herbs and spices",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Plants whose leaves or seeds are used as food or flavourings and sometimes for medicine. The rich variety of such plants in the Near East results in numerous references in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Aloes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:39-John19:40\">JHN 19:39–19:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:5-Num24:6\">NUM 24:5–24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6-Ps45:8\">PSA 45:6–45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17-Prov7:18\">PRO 7:17–7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:12-Song4:14\">SNG 4:12–4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Balm</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:11\">GEN 43:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25\">GEN 37:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:22\">JER 8:22</a></p>\n<h2>Bitter herbs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:5-Exod12:8\">EXO 12:5–12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:9-Num9:11\">NUM 9:9–9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:15\">LAM 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Caraway</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:27\">ISA 28:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:25\">ISA 28:25</a></p>\n<h2>Cassia</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:8\">PSA 45:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:22-Exod30:25\">EXO 30:22–30:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:19\">EZK 27:19</a></p>\n<h2>Cinnamon</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:22-Exod30:25\">EXO 30:22–30:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17-Prov7:18\">PRO 7:17–7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:12-Song4:14\">SNG 4:12–4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Coriander</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:31\">EXO 16:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:7\">NUM 11:7</a></p>\n<h2>Cummin</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:25\">ISA 28:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:27\">ISA 28:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a></p>\n<h2>Dill</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Henna</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:14\">SNG 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:13\">SNG 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Mint</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></p>\n<h2>Myrrh</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:12\">EST 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:13\">SNG 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38-John19:39\">JHN 19:38–19:39</a></p>\n<h2>Rue</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Saffron</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:13-Song4:14\">SNG 4:13–4:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Salt herbs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:1-Job30:5\">JOB 30:1–30:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Other spices</h2>\n<h3>Given as gifts or as tribute</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:10\">1KI 10:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:9\">2CH 9:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1-1Kgs10:2\">1KI 10:1–10:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:1\">2CH 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:25\">1KI 10:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:24\">2CH 9:24</a></p>\n<h3>Traded between countries</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25\">GEN 37:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:22\">EZK 27:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></p>\n<h3>Used in burial customs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:14\">2CH 16:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1\">MRK 16:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:56-Luke24:1\">LUK 23:56–24:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:40\">JHN 19:40</a></p>\n<h3>Used for perfume or flavouring</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:34-Exod30:35\">EXO 30:34–30:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:8\">PSA 75:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:10\">SNG 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:10\">EZK 24:10</a></p>\n<h3>Stores of spices</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:2\">ISA 39:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:29-1Chr9:30\">1CH 9:29–9:30</a></p>",
